lyrics:
Aw, rinna thuk nei ila,
Van angel-te nenin;
Chhandamna tuipui chhungah,
Thuruk awm en turin;
Awm dna pahnih inremin,
Amahah an luang hmun;
Infin lovin thianghlimin,
Famkim an awm dun.
Aw ka thla, thlir zel langin,
A mizia mak tak kha;
A hnenah i nun pein,
I phur amah bel la;
I chak lohna a hriatpui,
Mihring a nih vangin;
Lei leh vanah thu a nei,
Pathian nih vangin.
